qPCR was performed for primers:
- spanning exon 1 and 2 (ex1-2)
- exon 3 (ex3)
- spanning exon 4 and 5 (ex4-5)
- exon 6 (ex6)

In Figure 3e only results for exon6 were shown.

The qPCR results (ddCt values) used as input to generate the graph in panelE are in "ZFP608_ddCt_values_dC2-C3-AC2C3_for_anova.bed" file in this folder.
The statistical tests are in "ZFP608_ddCt_values_dC2-C3-AC2C3_for_anova.out" file.
